{
  "description": "Storage Location Mapping Template - Maps Excel location names to database IDs",
  "instructions": [
    "1. Query your storage_device table to get IDs and names",
    "2. Fill in the actual IDs from your database",
    "3. This mapping is OPTIONAL - if not provided, locations will be extracted from storage_path",
    "4. Format: 'Excel Location Name': {'id': <database_id>, 'type': 'device|shelf|rack|box'}"
